	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.10]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Arch Shielding<br>Increase Total Hit Points from 144 (L44) to 150 (L50)<br>Increase Armor Class (AC) from 26 (L44) to 27 (L48)<br>Increase Magic Resist by 20 (L44)<br><br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Classes: Nec (L44), Wiz (L44), Mag (L44), Enc (L44)<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Skill: Abjuration<br>Allowable Targets: Self<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Resistance Check: None<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Mana Required: 200<br>Spell Duration: 720 ticks (72.0 minutes)<br>Duration Formula: 3<br>Casting Time: 12.0 seconds<br>Spell Recovery: 2.25 seconds<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Spell cast on you: You feel armored.<br>Spell fades: Your shielding fades.<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Take A Look At My Dream Bard <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=53470" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=53470</a> </td></tr>
